  "description_short": "Santander Bank ATM at 222 Broadway in NYC's Financial District. Open 24 hours, accepts deposits, walk-up access.",
  "description_long": "Santander Bank, N.A. is an FDIC-insured bank operating a network of 2,000+ ATMs across the Northeast, including this Financial District location at 222 Broadway in New York. The bank offers comprehensive financial services including checking accounts, money market savings accounts, online and business banking, and investment services through affiliated brokers. This specific ATM location is a standalone walk-up machine available 24 hours daily with the ability to accept deposits, providing convenient cash access in lower Manhattan. The ATM is part of Santander's broader branch and ATM network, with nearby locations including a full branch at the same address and additional CVS-partnered ATMs within walking distance. Santander distinguishes itself through its extensive Northeast regional presence, integration with CVS Pharmacy locations for added convenience, and the availability of both digital banking (mobile app rated 4.7/5 stars) and in-person services. The bank emphasizes financial empowerment and inclusive sustainable growth through its Environmental, Social and Governance strategy. For consumers, this represents standard ATM functionality backed by a major FDIC-insured institution with robust digital banking options.",
